{
 "name": "RPlog_Post_Mortem",
 "title": "Post Mortem",
 "summary": "In the cavernous hangar bay of the ship Retribution, the Grand Admiral Axel and the Presav Crestian share drinks while the doctor Lynae Cassius performs a grim post-mortem examination on a set of bodies aboard a shuttle -- victims of the Sith Malus's handiwork. Axel admits he wanted Lynae to see Malus's work up close, unconcerned that it would faze the coolly clinical doctor. When Lynae returns with her synopsis, she identifies wounds consistent with stealth-trooper or intelligence wetwork, escalating into pleasure-killing mutilation. Resolving to spin a press release and track Malus down, Axel asks Lynae to alert him the instant the Sith makes contact or is spotted.",
